"**Cloud Log Manager**: Logs can be forwarded to the Nethesis Cloud Log "
"Manager (CLM) service."
msgstr ""
"**Cloud Log Manager**: I log possono essere inoltrati al servizio Nethesis "
"Cloud Log Manager (CLM)."

#: ../../logs.rst:17 fa1578d6ccc440c19d9a2c7e981cdfec
